en_192120_0	The Postal and Telecommunication Officers' Union says that they would launch a 2-day token strike from tomorrow midnight (Jun 03) over several demands including issues in the recruitment process.
en_192120_1	The General Secretary of the Union, H. K. Kariyawasam said that all postal officers would support this action.
en_192120_2	However, the Post Master General Rohana Abeyratne said that all steps have been taken to face the strike.
